Package: slurmSubmit
Title: Submit R Scripts to Slurm Clusters Remotely
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Bradley",
           role=c("aut","cre"),
           email = "mdb1296@gmail.com"
           )
Description: This package allows you to remotely submit R jobs Slurm clusters. As compared
            to similar packages, this package implements a formal S4 templates to allow users
            to save or cache successful job submissions.
            See the documentation for the submit() command for more details.
